Thank you to Manpower and Defence force Recruiting for ten remarkable years of success, friendship and learning. As I set my sights on future goals I had a moment to reflect on the past accomplishments made possible from my time here at DFR - what a whirlwind; from heavy demolition demonstrations, to VIP experiences with the CDF. I am everyday grateful for my professional achievements and look forward to what the next decade has to offer.
